omer support operations, we’ll provide each and everything you need for your convenience.</p></div></div></div></h3></div></div>', 'active', '2022-12-30 11:16:11', '2022-12-30 11:28:27'),
(2, 'Professional Approach to Quality Assurance', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px;\">To us, quality is everything and we don’t let our clients down. With professionalism and tenacity, we perform a 3-step QC process to maintain the top-notch quality of your image.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px;\">For seamless photo editing and retouching service, the CPS designers use pen tablets or stylus as well.</p>', 'active', '2022-12-30 11:28:46', '2022-12-30 11:46:54'),
(3, 'Be The Judge', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: &quot;Neue Einstellung&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">We don’t want you to stress over choosing us for your work. So that you can decide if the CPS is the perfect catalyst to get your photo post processing job, we have a free trial offer.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: &quot;Neue Einstellung&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Try our services for free before you decide to work with us. You can try up to three images in the free-trial offer.</p>', 'active', '2022-12-30 11:29:04', '2022-12-30 11:29:04'),
(4, 'Our Capacity', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px;\">Typical firms will let you down with their slow work. The ones that are fast will ruin the quality. We do it fast without the quality being compromised a bit. With our unique professionals, we nurture the images that give you a good quality impression.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px;\">Got a bulk amount of work? No worries, we’ll balance everything out so that you can save time while your quality is ensured.</p>', 'active', '2022-12-30 11:29:20', '2022-12-30 11:47:17'),
(5, 'With Skills, We Talk', '<p><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: &quot;Neue Einstellung&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">The Clipping Path Service (CPS) team, without a shadow of a doubt, is one of the greatest assets the image editing industry ever had. We’re one step ahead when it comes to using the latest post processing technology to create a long-lasting impression.</p><ul style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Neue Einstellung&quot;; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">We use all the major photo editing software that is required to fix all of your image editing problems.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">We ensure the true image color separation along with the dimensions and margins to resize image.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">Our photoshop experts will successfully deal with any photo post processing challenges you through at them with in-depth CMYK color knowledge.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">We spend an impressive amount of time researching and understanding the working materials.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">Combining the necessary information and bringing sketch conclusion is what we do seamlessly.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">We manage the time effectively and make sure you get the on-demand delivery.</li><li style=\"vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; border: 0px;\">We have high speed internet connection without any interruption for data transfer.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.33333rem; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: &quot;Neue Einstellung&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">In addition, you’ll get our complete support, reliability, and suggestions to help your business grow and take it to its peak.</p>', 'active', '2022-12-30 11:29:40', '2022-12-30 11:29:40'),
